    { 'uID': 1 }, 

    function(data) {
        $.each(data, function(i, item) {
            $("<span/>").html(item.time).html(".nowtime");
        });
    });

```

Needless to say, it doesn't work...could someone give me a hand with it and also explain what 
$("").html(item.time).html(".nowtime");
